ican}} |'''55%'''\n|\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} |John Murphy\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} align=\"right\" |12,250\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} |4.3%\n|\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} |James Bednarski\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} align=\"right\" |5,154\n|{{Party shading/Independent}} |1.8%\n|\n|-\n{{s-end}}\n\n==Personal Life==\nJoe and his wife Ginny have three children as well as four grandchildren.<ref>{{cite web|title=About Joe|url=http://www.pitts.house.gov/about-me/full-biography/short-biography}}</ref>\n\n==Bibliography==\n*{{cite book|url=http://web.archive.org/web/20030116123931/http://www.house.gov/pitts/press/commentary/020425c-stevens.htm|title=Thaddeus Stevens, A Man Before His Time|last=Pitts|first=Joe|date=April 24, 2002|work=Sixteenth Congressional District of Pennsylvania|publisher=United States House of Representatives|accessdate=January 16, 2003}}\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat-inline|Joe Pitts}}\n*[http://www.house.gov/pitts/ U.S. Congressman Joe Pitts] official U.S. House site\n*[http://www.joepittsforcongress.com/ Joe Pitts for Congress]\n*{{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Pennsylvania/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Joe_Pitts_%5BR-16%5D|Joe Pitts}}\n*{{CongLinks | congbio = p000373 | ballot = Joseph_R._Pitts | nndb = 743/000028659 | votesmart = 265 | govtrack = 400320 | opencong = 400320 | rollcall = 423 | politifact = joe-pitts | fec = H6PA16197 | opensecrets = N00001633 | assets = joseph-pitts | legistorm = 422/Rep_Joseph_Russell_Pitts.html | followthemoney = | ontheissues = PA/Joseph_Pitts.htm | congress = joseph-pitts/1514 | cspan = 11706 | imdb = 4372168 | bloomberg = | nyt = | washpo = gIQAOAMOAP }}\n*[http://www.sourcewatch.org/index.php?title=Joe_Pitts Profile] at [[SourceWatch]]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n|state=Pennsylvania\n|district=16\n|before=[[Robert Smith Walker]]\n|after=Incumbent\n|years=1997\u2013Present}}\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{